cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.HC 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision tasks, specifically social relation recognition from images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of graphs and reasoning, which could place it in cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
